# Loaded by `vite build --mode test` (see the `build:test` script).
#
# Production builds gate the `window.__test_store` Playwright harness hook on
# `import.meta.env.DEV`, which is false under any `vite build`. The browser test
# suite runs against a `vite preview` of a real build, so it needs that hook
# present without shipping it in the production bundle. This flag re-opens the
# gate for test-mode builds only; the default `pnpm build` never sees it.
VITE_EXPOSE_TEST_HOOKS=true
